embeds.title: That player doesn't have premium!
embeds.description: In order to view stats for 2026, a [premium plan](https://statalytics.net/premium) is required!

fields.name: How does it work?
fields.value:
`-` You can view any player's stats for 2026 if you have a premium plan.
 `-` You can view a player's stats for 2026 if they have a premium plan.
